Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that do not include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait grouped by country of the resource performing the activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call in traces where both activities occur consecutively or with intermediate steps
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between the start of Accepted + Wait and the end of Completed + In Call in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait in variants that transition directly to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait in variants containing Queued + Awaiting Assignment before Accepted + Wait versus those without
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait when preceded by Accepted + In Progress compared to when preceded by Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + In Progress occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Closed in cases that also contain Completed + In Call versus those that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum duration of Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that lead to Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait across all cases that eventually execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait in variants where Completed + In Call occurs earlier in the trace versus later
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress, specifically in traces that also include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait when the case originates from Brazil versus USA versus France
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country
